Homework 4: Projections

CSCI 5229: Gabriella Johnson


Instructions to use program:
a/d      Look left/right in the scene
w/s        Move forwards/backward into/from the scene
m          Toggle between view modes: perspective, orthogonal, and first person perspective
+/-        Changes field of view for perspective
x          Toggle axes
arrows     Change view angle
[  ]       Zoom in and out: decrease/increase dim
0          Reset view angle
ESC        Exit

Time it took to complete assignment: 8 hours
